value: "&aNo hay jugadores que necesiten ayuda actualmente!"
"&cNo tienes los items necesarios para revivir al jugador."
"&cThe confirmation time has expired. Use the command again."
"&cNo tienes permiso para usar este comando."
"&aYou can be revived if another player uses: &e/revive [NAME]"
"&e[NAME] &chas died and been banned for &e[DAYS] days&c. Someone can revive them with: &e/revive [NAME]"
"&cHas muerto por &e[DEATHS]&c vez y has sido baneado por &e[DAYS] dias&c."
"&7Tip: The player must have joined the server at least once."
"&e[NAME] &cha muerto y ha sido baneado por &e[DAYS] dias&c. Alguien puede revivirlo con: &e/revive [NAME]"
"&aPuedes ser revivido si otro jugador usa: &e/revive [NAME]"
"&cYou don't have permission to use this command."
"&cNo conozco a este jugador. Asegurate de escribir el nombre correctamente."
"&eAre you sure you want to revive [NAME]?"
"&cEl tiempo de confirmacion ha expirado. Usa el comando nuevamente."
"&eThis will cost you the following items: &a[ITEMS]"
"&cYou don't have the necessary items to revive the player."
"&7Tip: El jugador debe haber entrado al menos una vez al servidor."
"&cEl jugador &e[NAME] &cya esta vivo o no ha muerto aun."
"&cThe player &e[NAME] &cis already alive or hasn't died yet."
"&cI don't know this player. Make sure to spell the name correctly."
"&cYou have died for the &e[DEATHS]&c time and have been banned for &e[DAYS] days&c."
